Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.85,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃える緋の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:06.21,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}There I'll find my place
