Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:09.74,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}雷达之下寻找自己的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:16.24,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起钢刃
